E4Plus1.uk.description: The Daughter Also Rises: Lisa meets an intellectual romantic who shares her passion for culture. (S23 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: At Long Last Leave: The Simpsons are evicted from Springfield and join an off-grid community, but Marge and Homer meet hostility when they try to sneak back into town. (S23 Ep14/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Infestation Hypothesis: Amy is stuck in the middle of a battle of wills between Penny and Sheldon. Leonard and Priya try to spice up their long-distance relationship. (S5 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Pulled Groin Extrapolation: Leonard goes to a colleague's wedding as Amy's date. Howard tries to convince Bernadette to live with his mum after they get married. (S5 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Wiggly Finger Catalyst: Raj begins to get upset that he's the only one of the four guys not in a relationship, so Penny sets out to find him the perfect date. (S5 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Russian Rocket Reaction: Sheldon's old nemesis Wil Wheaton returns and invites everyone to a housewarming party. But Sheldon threatens to 'de-friend' Leonard if he attends. (S5 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Secrets of a Successful Marriage: Homer teaches a marriage guidance class but divulges a load of secrets about Marge and ends up in the doghouse. Or the tree house, at least. (S5 Ep22/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Treehouse of Horror XI: Homer receives a very scary horoscope, and Bart and Lisa are banished to the forest, where they find a house made of gingerbread... (S12 Ep1/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: E-I-E-I-(Annoyed Grunt): The Simpsons are forced to flee to the countryside, where Homer accidentally invents highly addictive tomacco. But the animals like it too... (S11 Ep5/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Marge Gamer: Marge gets hooked on an online fantasy game and discovers that Bart is the game's best - and most destructive - player. (S18 Ep17/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great Celebrity Bake Off...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...for Stand Up To Cancer: Danny Dyer, Rhod Gilbert, Leigh Francis and Yinka Bokinni make mini biscuit people and a fancy tea-time classic, and recreate their biggest failure in cake form.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Mission: Impossible - Fallout
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2018) Tom Cruise stars in part six of the action-thriller series. His mission: to stop terrorists from getting their hands on nuclear bombs and unleashing global devastation.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Workplace Proximity: Amy tells Sheldon she's been asked to work on a project at his university, but the guys insist that it will be bad for their relationship. (S7 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Romance Resonance: Sheldon is mortified when he stumbles upon an important scientific breakthrough by accident. Howard makes a romantic gesture to Bernadette. (S7 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: In the dating show that bares all, 20-year-old virgin Josh seeks a princess to help pop his cherry. And Matt and Mary look for a third person to join them in bed. (S3 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Burns' Heir: When Bart wins a competition to become Mr Burns' heir, he must choose between his boring family and the rich, over-indulgent power plant owner... (S5 Ep18/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: Carbon Dating and a Stuffed Raccoon: Sheldon gets into trouble with fellow child genius Paige at the Science Museum. Meemaw has a jumble sale in her garage. (S2 Ep7/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: An 8-Bit Princess and a Flat Tire Genius: Meemaw gives Sheldon his first video game. George Sr gets jealous when Georgie bonds with Herschel from the garage. (S2 Ep8/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Stand by Your Man: Dylan and Luke are impressed by Bill's tales of heroism as a firefighter, which makes Phil feel emasculated. So he invites the guys over for male bonding. (S10 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: The President's Fitness Test: Murray steps in when Adam asks Beverly to help him avoid the humiliation of taking a national physical fitness test at school. (S1 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: You're Not Invited: To help his little brother get his first kiss with Dana, Barry hosts a 'no parents allowed' birthday party in the basement for Adam. (S1 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Last Dance: The Butlers and Johnsons come together to support Marty in the aftermath of a major life change. (S5 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to New Beginnings: When a new local business uses Calvin's likeness without his permission, Dave volunteers to mediate on his friend's behalf. (S5 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Next Big Thing: Calvin and Marty consider starting a new business together. Dave sets up a small library stocked with a self-help book he wrote. (S5 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip from Rude Tube's naughty little sister Rude(ish) Tube, featuring sheep.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Million Dollar Reward: Adam yearns for independence, but Beverly struggles to let go. And Barry works hard to excel in medical school. (S10 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Worst Grinch Ever: Under pressure from their parents, Erica and Geoff must decide how to celebrate the holidays. And Adam learns that Brea has a new boyfriend. (S10 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Blade Runner: The Musical: Geoff and the JTP try to find a common connection while Adam directs the school play, and realises that dreams do come true. (S10 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Amadoofus: Beverly is pursued for a first date while Adam questions his friendship with Dave Kim. (S10 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Moms Need Other Moms: Beverly's child-rearing tactics seem unorthodox, while Barry and Adam concoct a plan to become more independent from their mother. (S10 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Lela's: In California, Gordon Ramsay visits Lela's, a fine dining restaurant run by inexperienced owner Lela and young chef Ricky. Can Gordon save them from complete disaster? (S1 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sebastian's: Gordon Ramsay visits Sebastian's, a pizzeria in Los Angeles. The customers are scarce and the debt is mounting. Can Gordon turn the restaurant's fortunes around? (S1 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Finn McCool's: Gordon Ramsay visits Finn McCool's, a traditional Irish pub in the Hamptons, where the family feuding has got out of hand. Can Gordon mediate? (S1 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Locomotion Reverberation: Leonard and Howard distract Sheldon with a trip to a historic railway when he slows their progress on the guidance system. (S10 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Allowance Evaporation: Amy is furious when she learns that Sheldon has shared intimate details of their relationship with his colleagues. (S10 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Comic-Con Conundrum: Cut off from his father's fortune, Raj appoints Sheldon to organise his finances. Penny considers joining the guys at Comic-Con. (S10 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Escape Hatch Identification: Leonard and Penny offer Sheldon's old room to Raj when he's forced to move out of his flat, leading to unexpected conflict. (S10 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Collaboration Fluctuation: Leonard, Penny and Raj settle into their new living arrangement, and Sheldon expresses an interest in Amy's professional life. (S10 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great Christmas Bake Off 2020
E4Plus1.uk.description: Paul Hollywood, Prue Leith, Matt Lucas and Tom Allen are joined by past bakers to celebrate Christmas in the tent. And Alexandra Burke performs her magical version of Silent Night.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Bumblebee
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2018) High-octane sci-fi action adventure starring Hailee Steinfeld. When Charlie drives home a clapped-out VW Beetle, she gets more than she bargained for: a huge robotic alien.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Hello Gutter, Hello Fadder: Homer bowls a perfect 300 and becomes a celebrity, even appearing on the Springfield Squares with Bumblebee Man and his old nemesis Ron Howard. (S11 Ep6/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Eight Misbehavin': Apu and Manjula take fertility drugs to get pregnant and end up with octuplets. Local companies shower them with gifts, until the Shelbyville Nine are born. (S11 Ep7/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sweet Seymour Skinner's Baadasssss Song: Bart gets Principal Skinner sacked and Flanders takes over at the school. Out of work, Skinner befriends his erstwhile nemesis Bart. (S5 Ep19/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Boy Who Knew Too Much: Bart is witness when Mayor Quimby's nephew is falsely accused of assaulting a French butler. But to testify, he has to admit to skipping school... (S5 Ep20/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Lady Bouvier's Lover: Grampa and Mr Burns compete for the affections of Marge's mum. (S5 Ep21/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Secrets of a Successful Marriage: Homer teaches a marriage guidance class but divulges a load of secrets about Marge and ends up in the doghouse. Or the tree house, at least. (S5 Ep22/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Treehouse of Horror XI: Homer receives a very scary horoscope, and Bart and Lisa are banished to the forest, where they find a house made of gingerbread... (S12 Ep1/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox Festive Special
E4Plus1.uk.description: Britain's sharpest armchair critics watch festive TV treats, from The Real Full Monty on Ice to The Sound of Music, Penguins: Meet the Family and Home Alone 2: Lost in New York. (S16 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: What do Britain's sharpest armchair critics think of Slow Horses, Dating Naked, Celebrity Race Across the World and more? (S24 Ep1) [SL]
